track_notes: Descent left to show alternate way to summit. Track represents section of the Art Loeb Trail, which passes over 5 SOTA summits.

Shortest route is from Camp Daniel Boone along the Art Loeb trail and then the Cold Mtn trail once you reach Deep Gap.  Hike is 5.6 miles with 2800 EG, with an easy grade on the 4 miles to Deep Gap and a moderate grade on the final climb to the summit.  Summit is a narrow ridgeline but there are several somewhat open areas where you can setup.  Parking for 10-12 vehicles along the road by the trailhead at 35.387407, -82.895930.
